Models are: 
1. Posts    join table = categories & users 
    belongs_to :user
    belongs_to :category 
    has_many :comments 
    has_many :users, through :comments
    
    
    attribues:
    title 
    content 

2. Users 
    has_many :posts 
    has_many :comments 
    has_many :commented_posts, through :comments
    has_many :categories, through :posts 

    attribues: 
    username
    email
    password_digest

3. Comment  join table = posts & users 
    belongs_to :user
    belongs_to :post 

    attribues:
    content 

4. categories 
     
    has_many :posts 
    has_many :users, through :posts 

    attribues:
    name

if you have webpacker missing error: do: 
    rails webpacker:install

webpacker requires yarn install: 
    npm install --global yarn 

To remove a git from directory 
    